15
00:01:03,430 --> 00:01:04,350
Ten years ago,

16
00:01:04,710 --> 00:01:06,230
soon after the incident
at the Duan mansion,

17
00:01:06,710 --> 00:01:07,400
I found Huaining

18
00:01:07,400 --> 00:01:09,350
injured and unconscious nearby.

19
00:01:10,120 --> 00:01:10,950
This jade pendant

20
00:01:11,310 --> 00:01:13,760
was on him then.

21
00:01:14,120 --> 00:01:15,710
But I never imagined

22
00:01:16,760 --> 00:01:18,870
that he is Duan's son.

23
00:01:19,480 --> 00:01:20,070
General,

24
00:01:20,840 --> 00:01:22,400
if Huaining really is Xunrui,

25
00:01:22,510 --> 00:01:24,350
why couldn't you recognize him
at that time?

26
00:01:24,560 --> 00:01:26,710
When I found him,
he had injuries all over his body.

27
00:01:27,000 --> 00:01:27,950
His face

28
00:01:28,200 --> 00:01:30,070
was burned beyond recognition.

29
00:01:30,480 --> 00:01:31,640
I hired doctors from overseas

30
00:01:31,640 --> 00:01:33,230
to save his life.

31
00:01:33,430 --> 00:01:34,400
When he woke up,

32
00:01:34,680 --> 00:01:36,760
he couldn't remember who he is.

33
00:01:39,200 --> 00:01:40,870
Xunrui.

34
00:01:40,920 --> 00:01:43,310
Xunrui.

35
00:01:48,480 --> 00:01:49,560
But you found him

36
00:01:49,560 --> 00:01:50,680
near the Duan mansion.

37
00:01:51,430 --> 00:01:53,680
The fire from that year spread far.

38
00:01:53,920 --> 00:01:56,120
How could I know whose child he was?

39
00:01:56,760 --> 00:01:57,680
At that time,

40
00:01:57,790 --> 00:02:00,560
I was utterly devastated by what happened

41
00:02:00,560 --> 00:02:01,710
to Duan and his family.

42
00:02:02,120 --> 00:02:03,640
If I had known that he is Xunrui,

43
00:02:03,950 --> 00:02:06,350
