44
00:02:06,640 --> 00:02:07,200
That...

45
00:02:07,790 --> 00:02:08,630
That jade pendant...

46
00:02:10,560 --> 00:02:11,590
Ten years ago,

47
00:02:12,710 --> 00:02:14,630
