48
00:02:15,310 --> 00:02:16,310
It is a pair.

49
00:02:17,470 --> 00:02:19,750
Impossible. I can't be Xunchu's brother.

50
00:02:24,120 --> 00:02:25,590
When the incident happened,

51
00:02:26,120 --> 00:02:27,800
