52
00:02:28,520 --> 00:02:29,590
Now that you two brothers

53
00:02:29,590 --> 00:02:31,150
are alive and reunited,

54
00:02:31,630 --> 00:02:34,710
I suppose I didn't let Duan down.

55
00:02:35,750 --> 00:02:36,470
Xunchu.

56
00:02:38,150 --> 00:02:38,710
Huaining.

57
00:02:39,800 --> 00:02:40,800
On my brother's back

58
00:02:40,800 --> 00:02:42,630
